	<text xml:lang="la">
		<note xml:id="fn1" type="footnote" subtype="metadata" n="1">Das Jahr ergibt sich aus dem für 1545 bezeugten Besuch von <persName ref="p8516" cert="high">Gerhard Westerburg</persName> und Jan (Johannes) Maczynski in <placeName ref="l587" cert="high">Zürich</placeName>; s. <hi>Pelikan,</hi> Chronikon 171, und <bibl source="b288">HBD</bibl> 33, 8f.</note>
		<body>
			<div xml:id="div1" corresp="regest1">
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la">S.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la">Qui has reddunt, vir clarissime, duo praestantes sunt amici vestrae ecclesiae, quorum alter, qui senior est, multis afflictionibus et longo exilio agitatus, <persName ref="p8516">Gerardus Westerburgius</persName><note xml:id="fn2" type="footnote" n="2">Siehe oben <ref target="file12243">Nr. 2196</ref>, Anm. 4.</note> est, vir notus doctis et piis.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la">Tecum et coeteris cum fratribus variis de negociis ecclesię<note xml:id="fna" type="footnote" n="a">ecclesiæ <hi>über der Zeile nachgetragen.</hi></note> ut colloquatur, ad vos<pb type="edition" next="408"/> proficiscitur.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la">Alter <placeName ref="l2472">Polonus</placeName>, iuvenis<note xml:id="fn3" type="footnote" n="3"><persName ref="p5929">Jan (Johannes) Maczyñski</persName>; s. oben <ref target="file12243">Nr. 2196</ref>, Anm. 7.</note> magnae spei, qui literis Hebraicis apud vos daturus operam est, tibi commendatus esse cupit.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la">Utrumque igitur pro tua singulari humanitate benigne si tractaveris, rem tui ingenii excellenti bonitate dignam et his gratam feceris<note xml:id="fn4" type="footnote" n="4">Siehe oben <ref target="file12243">Nr. 2196</ref>, Anm. 12. - <persName ref="p8516">Westerburg</persName> und <persName ref="p5929">Maczyñski</persName> trafen am 22. Juli 1545 in <placeName ref="l587">Zürich</placeName> ein; s. <hi><persName ref="p8127">Pellikan</persName>,</hi> Chronikon 171.</note>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la">Quod vero ad me attinet, ultro oblatam hanc ad te scribendi occasionem negligere nolui, quod, meum adversus te studium boni ut consulas, vehementer opto.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" ana="farewell">Vale, vir optime, cum omnibus <placeName ref="l587">Tigurinae</placeName> ecclesię ministris, quibus in Christo pręclara omnia precor.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la">18. iulii.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la"><persName ref="p8298">Martinus Borrhaus</persName> tuus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Adresse auf der Rückseite:]</note>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la">Clarissimo pietate et doctrina viro <persName ref="p495">Henrici Bull[in]gero</persName><note xml:id="fnb" type="footnote" n="b"><hi>Textverlust durch Papierverlust am rechten Rand des Blattes.</hi></note>, suo in Christo d. et fratri observando.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
	</text>
